{"tid":2099590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國共產黨黨魁「拜登」：當選總統第一日就重新加入世衛！","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:35:56.000Z","uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"480efc4c14964f3cd214bc2d22fedf72fb127784","tid":2099590,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:35:13.000Z","msg":"「法國國際廣播」美國國會已經正式收到特朗普政府關於退出世衛組織的通知。<span style=\"color: red;\">美國民主黨總統候選人拜登則表示，選舉成功在他總統任期&ldquo;第一天&rdquo;他將宣布美國&ldquo;返回&rdquo;世衛組織。</span><br />\n<br />\n今年5月底，美國總統唐納德&middot;特朗普曾表示：&ldquo;我們終止了與世界衛生組織（WHO）的關係。&rdquo; 特朗普指出，美國希望與中國建立&ldquo;開放和建設性&rdquo;關係，但這樣做的同時也應保護國家利益。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，&ldquo;中國政府沒有兌現對我們和其他許多國家的承諾。這些顯而易見的事實不容被忽視或被擱置&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/cn/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B4%25B2/20200707-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2594%25B1%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E6%2525B4%2525B2%2F20200707-%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E6%2525AD%2525A3%2525E5%2525BC%25258F%2525E9%252580%252580%2525E5%252587%2525BA%2525E4%2525B8%252596%2525E8%2525A1%25259B%2525E7%2525B5%252584%2525E7%2525B9%252594-%2525E6%25258B%25259C%2525E7%252599%2525BB%2525E5%252594%2525B1%2525E5%25258F%25258D%2525E8%2525AA%2525BF&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=2a4abdb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/cn/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B4%25B2/20200707-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2594%25B1%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF</a>"},{"pid":"48ba0e31d9dfb017ca785cb0013197f8b274ef7b","